  "common": {
    "name": {
      "zh": "ANA Tactical Alpha胸挂",
      "en": "ANA Tactical Alpha chest rig (Olive Drab)"
    },
    "shortName": {
      "zh": "Alpha",
      "en": "Alpha"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "高品质的\"Alpha\"胸挂，完全符合军用可靠性和功能性标准。一体化口袋和MOLLE背带的组合提供了携带大量必要装备的手段，是一款经典设计的战术胸挂。这种胸挂在设计时，将所有的装备都置于前方以及侧方，而背后部分由调整带及背带组成。",
      "en": "\"Alpha\" is a high-quality chest rig that fully meets the military standards for reliability and functionality. The combination of integrated pouches and MOLLE straps provides the means of carrying a large number of necessary equipment. The vest is designed as a classic chest rig. In this type of vest, all the gear is located in the front and side parts, while the back part is comprised of adjustment belts and straps. Manufactured by ANA Tactical."
    },
    "weight": 1.7,
    "width": 4,
    "height": 4,
    "rarity": "Superrare",
